### Get subscription tiers and save the first ID
GET {{host}}/api/subscriptions/tiers
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Accept: application/json

> {%
    if (response.status === 200 && response.body.length > 0) {
        client.global.set("tierId", response.body[0].id);
        client.log("Saved Tier ID: " + response.body[0].id);
    }
%}

### Purchase the Premium Subscription
POST {{host}}/api/subscriptions/purchase/{{tierId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Check my current active subscription
GET {{host}}/api/subscriptions/my-subscription
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Accept: application/json